  "title": "Customer Service Officer (Urgent!/ Up $17/h)",
  "description": "<p><strong>The Opportunity</strong></p><ul><li>Exciting opportunity to be part of the Entertainment and Gaming services sector</li><li>Duration: 1 year (renewable)</li><li>Weekdays: $12.50–$16/hr | Weekends: $13.50–$17/hr (higher pay after 11pm)</li><li>Location: Chinatown MRT</li><li>Must commit to a minimum of one weekend and one weekday (additional days/hours are welcome)</li></ul><p><strong>Job description:</strong></p><ul><li>Sell prize-related tickets and services at the counter</li><li>Handle prize claims and charity ticket transactions</li><li>Support customer onboarding and perform KYC verification</li><li>Carry out daily cash and ticket reconciliation</li><li>Maintain safety protocols and deliver quality customer service</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Able to communicate clearly and work well in a team</li><li>Well-presented, proactive, and positive in customer interactions</li><li>Able to commit to at least 1 midnight shift</li></ul><p><strong>Next Step</strong></p><p>Prepare your updated resume, send to the following email: eugene.chia@adecco.com or contact +65 87230071 for quick response</p><p>*Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted*<br /></p><p>Eugene Chia</p><p>Direct Line: 6697 7809</p><p>EA License No: 91C2918</p><p>Personnel Registration Number: R24124644</p>",
